response.original_title: Jimmy Jones: A Cultural Night Out
response.overview: Jimmy Jones demonstrates his adult humour in front of a live audience at the Lakeside Club in Camberley.  One of Britain's best comedians of the last 30 years.  This video displays Jimmy's talent for holding no punches as he goes for the jugular, from great side splitting send ups to tales to make your mother, father and all other relatives blush!  For those who are fans of Jimmy Jones this is a must, for those who don't know him or can't get the chance to see him buy this and see what comedy and laughter really is!
response.title: Jimmy Jones: A Cultural Night Out
